---
// Component for the brand story section
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section class='py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-background text-foreground'>
  <div class='container px-4 md:px-6'>
    <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center'>
      <div class='text-center md:text-left'>
        <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6'>
          從黑標王到 Black Living
        </h2>
        <p class='text-lg text-muted-foreground md:text-xl mb-8'>
          我們從專營席夢思「黑標」床墊起家，憑藉對品質的堅持與對客戶的承諾，
          成為蝦皮第一賣家。現在，我們將服務範圍擴展至整個居家生活領域，
          致力於為每個家庭打造舒適的睡眠環境。
        </p>
        <div
          class='flex justify-center md:justify-start items-center space-x-8 text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-4'
        >
          <span>🖤</span>
          <span>🌙</span>
          <span>🏠</span>
        </div>
        <p class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>Black (黑) • Moon (月亮) • Living (生活)</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Image
          src='https://placehold.co/800x600?text=about+blackliving'
          alt='About Black Living'
          width={800}
          height={600}
          class='rounded-lg object-cover w-full h-auto'
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
